Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.17,0:00:58.62,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}第一具有记载的灭火器\N出现在中世纪的欧洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.73,0:01:02.81,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它就像用来对火喷水的巨型注射器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.93,0:01:06.30,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现代灭火器用压缩空气来当堆进剂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.17,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}灭火物质可能是水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.41,0:01:12.17,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}或是化学液体,粉末或泡沫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.02,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}按压控制杆会打开释放阀\N而释放出压缩空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.25,0:01:22.97,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}压力会推动化学物质\N透过软管从喷嘴喷出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.38,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}为制造释放阀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.50,0:01:29.09,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们从叫做毛胚的铝制圆柱开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.30,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一个转盘使每个毛胚通过\N16个不同的切削站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.14,0:01:35.10,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}到了每一站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.22,0:01:40.14,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}在润滑液的润滑之下\N工具会为毛胚塑形6点5秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.41,0:01:46.26,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}每个毛胚巡回一周后就会离开转盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.89,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}从毛胚到做成释放阀只要1分钟15秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.13,0:01:59.09,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在他们将灭火器的铝制把手\N铆接在阀上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.21,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它以一根销为枢轴转动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.33,0:02:11.46,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接着他们将铝制控制杆铆接到把手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.41,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这就是你使用灭火器时\N要按压的控制杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.29,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}然后再装上阀杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.34,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它是阀的内部零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.21,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}工人只需把它放进里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.22,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一台自动组装机就完成剩下的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.57,0:02:34.50,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它将弹簧放在阀杆上\N在你按压控制杆时带来阻力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.98,0:02:42.06,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接着加一个扣件\N将阀杆和弹簧固定在定位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.98,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在工人套上塑胶套管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.09,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}来定位接着摆上的橡胶O型环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.21,0:02:53.57,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}O型环是在阀与圆筒之间\N作密封之用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.25,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}让内容物不会外泄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.10,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}虹吸管从阀插入圆筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.18,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}灭火的化学物质就是沿着这管子往上\N然后从喷嘴喷出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.65,0:03:07.37,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}圆筒内的压缩空气会推进化学物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:11.22,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这个压力表显示\N压力是否足以发挥这个作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.70,0:03:15.66,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}在将压力表的螺纹柄涂上密封剂\N以防止漏气后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.69,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们将它旋紧在释放阀上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.29,0:03:21.29,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}释放阀组件现在已完成组装及测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.18,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}准备好装在圆筒顶端了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.41,0:03:30.65,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}为了装上它\N圆筒必须要有一个螺纹环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.90,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}工人使用冲床将它固定在圆筒上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.22,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}圆筒也需要底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.73,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}工厂用来永久熔接底部\N和螺蚊环的技术叫做铜焊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.94,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它和焊接相似\N只是用了一个铜环作为黏接金属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.33,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}在将铜焊环放进未封闭的圆筒底部后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.62,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们压入钢制的底座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.82,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}然后他们将铜焊环放在螺纹环上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.66,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在要送进铜焊火炉烤1小时45分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:15.05,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}摄氏1100度的高温熔化两个铜环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.33,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}结合它们所连结的组件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.93,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}下一站是静电油漆房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.42,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们在此把正电荷加在油漆粒子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.70,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}也把负电荷加在圆筒上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.93,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这会让油漆均匀吸附在表面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.13,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接着圆筒被送入烤箱45分钟来烘漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.49,0:04:45.78,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}圆筒一冷却后\N自动机器就为它们填充灭火粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.13,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}主要材料是一种氨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.05,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}当你把它喷在火上时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.09,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}热会熔化微粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.34,0:04:57.78,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}使它们形成阻绝氧气的覆盖层\N因而闷熄火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.01,0:05:01.85,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}填充完后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.97,0:05:06.05,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一台自动机器将阀\N旋上每个圆筒的螺纹环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.78,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在该是为圆筒加压的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.14,0:05:18.06,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们按压控制杆来打开阀\N让压缩机能为圆筒注气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.90,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}他们持续充气直到压力到达13巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.89,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这相当于汽车胎压的六倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.85,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接着他们旋上喷嘴并装上锁销
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.89,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这会锁住控制杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.01,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}让灭火器不会不小心喷出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.41,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一如说明贴纸说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.13,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}发生火灾时\N你只需抽出锁销并对准火喷洒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.30,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这个固定架\N使你能把灭火器挂在方便取得的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.30,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这样一有需要就可以随时取用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.71,0:06:04.27,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}甜甜圈以前叫油糕\N因为当时是用猪油炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.99,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}当荷兰清教徒把它们带来美国时\N它们是球形的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.35,0:06:12.19,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}但很快有人发现\N从中间拿掉一球生面团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.12,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}会使它炸得更均匀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.76,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}因此甜甜圈就诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.83,0:06:27.07,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}甜甜圈基本上可分为两种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.95,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}酵母甜甜圈和蛋糕甜甜圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.27,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}蛋糕甜甜圈的面糊\N从搅拌器直接掉进沸腾的蔬菜油里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.63,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}喷嘴会在面团通过时塑形面团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.40,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}甜甜圈要炸上约一分钟半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.76,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}然后输送带把它们从缸里带出来降温
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.40,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}酵母甜甜圈要花比较多时间制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.92,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一台高速搅拌器搅拌酵母面团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.04,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接着工人将面团拉入箱子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.32,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它接下来进入给料器\N这会将面团挤压成片状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.67,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}然后它被送到了另一条输送带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.79,0:07:20.36,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这里一连串的滚筒\N将面团片压到只有两公分厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.27,0:07:37.63,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}接下来面团片通过洒下的肉桂粉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.44,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}然后一根旋转圆柱把面团卷成圆条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.87,0:07:46.88,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一条小金属棒在面团上洒水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.68,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这使它保持湿黏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.28,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}让它能保持形状\N来通过另一个滚筒进行压薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.07,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}洒上玉米淀粉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.04,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}让现在把面团切块的刀片\N不会沾黏到面团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.12,0:08:16.52,CHS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\1c&H00FFFF&}伸缩机械臂将面团块\N一次四块地放在金属网托盘上
